race.comment: JAM PACKED (4) went down by the narrowest of margins at Eagle Farm last time out and looks to be knocking on the door of a maiden victory. Lerena sticks in the saddle following the past few outings and strikes a winnable contest here. Rates the testing material. BRIEF SPIRIT (1) just ran into one better at the latest run and gets plenty of weight relief with the 3kg claim. Looms as the main danger. MAN TALK (5) hasn't been too far away in recent efforts and will be rock-hard fit for this. Top-three claims. ZOUSOUL (3) is drawn to get a gun run from the inside alley and may earn some minor money. SILVIO DANTE (2) best of the rest.
